# This file lists the installed Stanford CoreNLP language model JARs.
# It is populated by the data_manager_corenlp_models data manager.
# Each line is a model with the following tab-separated columns:
#   <value>  <name>  <lang_code>  <version>  <models_path>
#
# - value: unique identifier (typically the language code)
# - name: display name shown to users
# - lang_code: CoreNLP language code (ar, zh, en, fr, de, hu, it, es; "common" for the shared JAR)
# - version: CoreNLP version the JAR is compatible with
# - models_path: absolute path to the language model JAR file
#
# Example entries (populated automatically by the data manager):
#
#en	English	en	4.5.10	/path/to/corenlp/4.5.10/stanford-corenlp-4.5.10-models-english.jar
#fr	French	fr	4.5.10	/path/to/corenlp/4.5.10/stanford-corenlp-4.5.10-models-french.jar
